<html xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_1_0.xsd"
	xmlns:p="tapestry:parameter">

<body>
	<h1><i>cache/Container</i> component sample :</h1>
	
	<p>
	This component provides caching of the generated HTML for a page snippet in EHCache.
	</p>
	
	<h2>Render duration for 500 ActionLinks : </h2>
	<hr/>
	<div t:type="ActionLinkLoop" t:nbElements="500"></div>
	
	<h3>Code snippet:</h3>
	<pre>
		<code>
			${codeSnippet}
		</code>
	</pre>
	Do not forget the dependency to <i>tapestry-caching</i> library in your <i>pom.xml</i>:
	<pre>
		<code>
			${pomDependency}
		</code>
	</pre>
</body>
</html>